{"tid":2495082,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"28歲男愛吃半熟肉惹寄生蟲上身，肚屙半年揭大腸藏3絛蟲蠕動至肛門","createTime":"2021-04-19T03:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T03:54:03.000Z","uid":278587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e902e73c37df1e21db114f3c65076e4a005e8a1e","tid":2495082,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2932924/0047a69c-8e38-44b9-b803-dea0d7092fc7_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2932924%2F0047a69c-8e38-44b9-b803-dea0d7092fc7_1024.jpg&h=46ecf64e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2932924/2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2932924%2F2_600.jpg&h=c97ec42b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2932924/3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2932924%2F3_600.jpg&h=52db8844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛食生肉，恐增加感染寄生蟲風險！一名愛食生牛肉的男子因長期腸胃痛及腹瀉半年求醫，經檢查發現腸道有絛蟲寄生。醫生提醒民眾，應食用已煮熟的肉類，以及不要生吃淡水魚類，以免感染寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n台灣直腸外科醫生蕭慕琦日前在Facebook專頁分享病例指，一名28歲外籍男子入境到台灣工作，完成14天居家檢疫後到醫院接受健康檢查。當時，男子提到之前經常出現腸胃痛，且長期腹瀉長達半年。蕭醫生為患者進行大腸鏡檢查，發現乙狀結腸處有3條「如白麵條」的絛蟲正在蠕動。她隨即透過夾子，將絛蟲取出，惟在取蟲過程中，絛蟲斷成一半，消失不見蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n蕭醫生表示，絛蟲分為豬肉絛蟲、牛肉絛蟲及廣節裂頭絛蟲，寄生於人體的小腸，可生長至數米長。牠們是「節片式繁殖」，即使斷裂仍可一截截的繁殖生長。當日所見的蟲體應為斷裂後的節片，正往肛門移動，準備排泄出去後，繼續尋找其他寄主，<br />\n<br />\n「今日所見的蟲體，應該是裂解出來的節片，準備向肛門移動，前往『新世界』『開枝散葉』。所以當便便的時候，看到伴隨著類似麵條的東西，要小心喔......」<br />\n<br />\n她又指，夾出的2段絛蟲節片放在水中時，後段像魚尾左右擺動。隨後，蕭醫生將患者轉介至感染科，藉藥物治療將絛蟲的頭排出。她研判，男子應是愛食用生牛肉或未熟的牛肉，導致牛肉絛蟲轉寄生於人體。蕭醫生提醒，腸胃發育未完全的孩童以及免疫力較差的成年人平時應盡量少生食，且肉類要煮至全熟及不要生吃淡水魚類，以免寄生蟲感染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2932924/病從口入｜28歲男愛吃半熟肉惹寄生蟲上身%20肚屙半年揭大腸藏3絛蟲蠕動至肛門\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2932924%2F%E7%97%85%E5%BE%9E%E5%8F%A3%E5%85%A5%EF%BD%9C28%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E6%84%9B%E5%90%83%E5%8D%8A%E7%86%9F%E8%82%89%E6%83%B9%E5%AF%84%E7%94%9F%E8%9F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%BA%AB%2520%E8%82%9A%E5%B1%99%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%8F%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%85%B8%E8%97%8F3%E7%B5%9B%E8%9F%B2%E8%A0%95%E5%8B%95%E8%87%B3%E8%82%9B%E9%96%80&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=9078fcaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2932924/病從口入｜28歲男愛吃半熟肉惹寄生蟲上身%20肚屙半年揭大腸藏3絛蟲蠕動至肛門</a>"},{"pid":"750c1d5288e405e6d9ff201acdd7401e0cc753c6","tid":2495082,"uid":321977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"你老母呢啲就有大圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5679caa61687aa4a3699ab319faf38ef94a73667","tid":2495082,"uid":85552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdC3Ff9sGD2rCemK6LLjVoD5JJiufmiz794hWdQQQSUxF?filename=bPyjhKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPyjhKH.jpg&h=5e90bdf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab21faa805494e1d702921eeba590f0c33548eff","tid":2495082,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:47:43.000Z","msg":"日本人都唔食生文魚啦<br />\n<br />\n佢地好熟將d生冷野出晒口<br />\n<br />\n自己食熟野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而香港人就鍾意食生冷野"},{"pid":"6817873438d1c4caff3d8f140c15b6fb88f8a7c6","tid":2495082,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"好細個個陣返大陸拜山試過痾蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣無座廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部都係踎廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痾完一篤勁大篤既屎之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到篤屎上面有好多好幼既白色條狀物係到蠕動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00b2afe8f524949d01edc7739bd10647b6dc026","tid":2495082,"uid":32615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab21faa805494e1d702921eeba590f0c33548eff","tid":2495082,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:47:43.000Z","msg":"日本人都唔食生文魚啦<br />\n<br />\n佢地好熟將d生冷野出晒口<br />\n<br />\n自己食熟野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而香港人就鍾意食生冷野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:54:03.000Z","msg":"生文魚唔食日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}